message: There are many papers that discuss biomarkers in colorectal cancer and translational proteomics research. Some of the most notable papers include "Biomarkers in Colorectal Cancer: A Review of Proteomics-Based Approaches" by J.M. Gómez-López et al., "Translational Proteomics in Colorectal Cancer: A Review" by M.A. Sánchez-García et al., and "Biomarkers in Colorectal Cancer: A Review of Clinical and Molecular Aspects" by M.A. Sánchez-García et al. Additionally, there are many other papers that discuss the use of biomarkers in colorectal cancer and translational proteomics research. Do you have any specific questions about any of these papers?
speaker: RAVEN
